name: Wrapped USDT (Sollet)
description:
wUSDT (Wrapped USDT) is a tokenized representation of Tether (USDT), backed 1:1 by the original asset. It is designed for use on blockchains other than the native USDT network, ensuring compatibility with decentralized applications (dApps), smart contracts, and DeFi protocols.
wUSDT preserves the stability of USDT while enabling enhanced interoperability and seamless integration within multi-chain ecosystems.
